sentence:
There are so many things wrong with what you said that it is impossible to detail them all here, but: 
a) there are very few problems caused by cannabis and very many problems caused by cannabis prohibition;
b) "pot people" will obey the law when the law obeys them and not before;
c) cannabis is not terrible, nor is it a gateway drug, as has been proven again and again and as I am sure you well know (because you're probably a troll);
d) murder for cannabis is a black market thing so that is an argument FOR re-legalization not for prohibition;
e) cannabis has been documented to provide numerous health benefits and it has many healing properties, which I am sure you also already know (because now I'm really sure you're a troll);
